      "region": {
        "ja": "京都",
        "en": "Kyoto"
      },
      "kanji": "京都",
      "meta": {
        "ja": "洛中・洛東 ／ 9軒掲載",
        "en": "Kyoto · 9 logged"
      },
      "cafes": [
        {
          "cat": {
            "ja": "コーヒーショ",
            "en": "Coffee Shop"
          },
          "name": {
            "ja": "Goodman Roaster Kyoto",
            "en": "Goodman Roaster Kyoto"
          },
          "type": {
            "ja": "Specialty Coffee Roaster",
            "en": "Specialty Coffee Roaster"
          },
          "ward": {
            "ja": "京都・下京区",
            "en": "Shimogyō, Kyoto"
          },
          "blurb": {
            "ja": "台湾・台北で絶大な人気を誇るロースタリーの京都店。創業者自ら農家と直接取引する、世界最高峰の台湾・阿里山（アリサン）産コーヒーを、洗練されたライトローストで堪能できます。",
            "en": "The Kyoto branch of a highly acclaimed Taipei-based roaster. Discover world-class Taiwanese Alishan coffee, sourced directly from farmers and served in a beautifully refined light roast."
          },
          "order": {
            "ja": "",
            "en": ""
          },
          "owner": {
            "ja": "伊藤 篤臣",
            "en": "Atuomi Ito"
          },
          "bio": {
            "ja": "スターバックス等でのキャリアを経て、台湾・阿里山コーヒーの浅煎りの風味に衝撃を受け単身台湾へ。台北の空港の小さなスペースから「Goodman Roaster」をスタートさせ、瞬く間に人気ブランドへと成長。2019年、念願の日本1号店を古都・京都にオープンした。",
            "en": "After working as a barista in Japan, he moved to Taiwan, captivated by the vibrant light roasts of Alishan coffee. He launched Goodman Roaster in Taipei, later expanding to Kyoto in 2019."
          },
          "awards": {
            "ja": "",
            "en": ""
          },
          "killer": {
            "ja": "ネルドリップで引き出す深く丸い余韻",
            "en": "A deep, round finish drawn through nel drip"
          },
          "features": {
            "ja": "",
            "en": ""
          },
          "access": {
            "ja": "京都市営地下鉄烏丸線「四条駅」から徒歩約5分、阪急京都線「烏丸駅」から徒歩約6分（綾小路通りを西へ、西洞院通りの手前）",
            "en": "A 5-minute walk from Shijo Station, or a 6-minute walk from Karasuma Station."
          },
          "img": "/images/Goodmancoffee.jpg",
          "hp": "https://goodmanroaster.com/"
        },
        {
          "cat": {
            "ja": "",
            "en": ""
          },
          "name": {
            "ja": "COYOTE the ordinary shop",
            "en": "COYOTE the ordinary shop"
          },
          "type": {
            "ja": "El Salvador Speciality Coffee Shop",
            "en": "El Salvador Speciality Coffee Shop"
          },
          "ward": {
            "ja": "京都・京都駅前",
            "en": "Kyoto Station,Kyoto"
          },
          "blurb": {
            "ja": "エルサルバドルのコーヒーだけを取り扱う唯一無二のコーヒーショップ。現地の農園とダイレクトに繋がり、生産者のストーリーとともにここでしか飲めない、希少なコーヒーを楽しめます",
            "en": "A one-of-a-kind coffee shop specializing exclusively in El Salvadorian coffee. Sourced directly from local farms, it offers rare coffees you won't find anywhere else, served alongside the unique stories of the producers."
          },
          "order": {
            "ja": "ドリップ：Don Jaime Pacamara",
            "en": "Pour-over: Don Jaime Pacamara"
          },
          "owner": {
            "ja": "門川 雄輔",
            "en": "Yusuke Kadokawa"
          },
          "bio": {
            "ja": "新卒で小川珈琲株式会社に入社。営業職として働いた後、JICA（国際協力機構）の隊員としてエルサルバドルのコーヒー農園に1年半滞在。コロナ禍での現地の危機をきっかけに2020年に創業。2021年7月に初の店舗として京都駅前にオープンした。",
            "en": "After graduating, he joined Ogawa Coffee as a sales representative. He then spent a year and a half working at coffee farms in El Salvador as a JICA (Japan International Cooperation Agency) volunteer. Driven to support producers during the crisis of the pandemic, he founded COYOTE in 2020 and opened this first branch near Kyoto Station in July 2021."
          },
          "awards": {
            "ja": "",
            "en": ""
          },
          "killer": {
            "ja": "",
            "en": ""
          },
          "features": {
            "ja": "",
            "en": ""
